---
source: tests/cli_help.rs
expression: normalize_help_output(&stdout)
---
Search Spotify and play the first matching result

Usage: spotuify play [OPTIONS] <QUERY>

Arguments:
  <QUERY>  Search query

Options:
      --type <KIND>      Media type to search [default: track] [possible values: all, track, episode, album, artist, playlist]
      --format <FORMAT>  Output format for the mutation receipt [default: table] [possible values: table, json, jsonl, csv, ids]
  -h, --help             Print help
